        <abstract>
            <para>The dataset is part of the effort to provide the most detailed climate data for
                CAPLTER and related projects. This dataset represents average monthly
                maximum/minimun air temperature derived from spatial interpolation of daily
                temperature data from a dense network of meteorological sensors for the period of 6
                years (2000-2005).</para>
